COUNTMSB EQU H'0021'	;MSB PORTION OF THE 16 BIT COUNTER FOR TMR2 INTERRUPTS
SERVOPOS EQU H'0022'	;8-BIT SERVO POSITION NUMBER
COMMAND EQU H'0023'	;Stores the command mode received from UART 


